Tyrael looked at the ship and marvelled. It was a very new warship 
design, probably one of those under construction when he had left the 
Headquarters to chase those Predacons. It was bristling with weapons 
and would probably land safely too. After his mission was done, they 
could get down to the pacification of Cybertron, he thought.
